Interface FormatIdentificationPlugin


  • public interface FormatIdentificationPlugin
    Interface for the FormatIdentificationPlugin type.
    The plugin performs file format identification
    This plugin interface only supports java implementation.

      • identifyFormat

        FormatIdentificationResult identifyFormat(java.lang.String filePath)
        Performs the file format identification. Return result that contain a list of format matches and the relevant format identification method (SIGNATURE, CONTAINER or EXTENSION)
        Parameters:
        - - filePath - the path to the file that needs format identification
        Returns:
